  "description": "<b>苹果已经开始调整其iPhone5的维修政策，主要是iPhone5屏幕更换服务，取代以往的整机更换。外媒报道，除了屏幕修理外，苹果还将提供其他方面的故障服务，比如相机、电源键等，实施的时间定在了7月份。</b>那么iPhone5在国内的维修政策是否也是如此呢？《IT时报》记者从苹果旗舰店了解到，目前上海地区的苹果零售店都还没有接到通知，上海的三家苹果零售店仍在继续执行4月份下发的维修政策。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d5faf13/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241363.htm&amp;t=iPhone5%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4+%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%BA%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241363.htm&amp;t=iPhone5%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4+%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%BA%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241363.htm&amp;t=iPhone5%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4+%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%BA%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241363.htm&amp;t=iPhone5%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4+%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%BA%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241363.htm&amp;t=iPhone5%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4+%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%BA%E5%B0%9A%